{"tid":458412,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【送廢老上路】血庫極缺！現僅能應付50%需求！","createTime":"2017-11-04T22:21:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-06T11:04:35.000Z","uid":29314,"like":85,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":86,"replies":[{"pid":"2181c376bb8e4012a249df5c0a28efa56f354623","tid":458412,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T22:21:33.000Z","msg":"2017年11月5日<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n紅十字會輸血服務中心指，上周五（3日）只有903人捐血，成功收集663袋血液。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不過由於全港醫院的血液使用量一直高企</span></span>，現時中心血庫的所有血型存量，包括O正、A正和B正均極度短缺，並且長時間徘徊警戒水平，現時儲存水平僅能應付預算需要使用量的一半，緊急呼籲捐血。"},{"pid":"b9162160c6d33811ab4d92c4076c80194d77e02f","tid":458412,"uid":29314,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T22:22:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171104/large/1509762829_5f00.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171104%2Flarge%2F1509762829_5f00.jpg&h=21a3b9f2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"af0cc8660fdbf7be061bc3561dd6c4a12f4887f0","tid":458412,"uid":69886,"like":37,"dislike":2,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T22:28:57.000Z","msg":"個人會虧，不了"},{"pid":"d3903a012235bd16bf390315ef8ed1e669f927da","tid":458412,"uid":126102,"like":101,"dislike":1,"score":100,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T22:38:24.000Z","msg":"咁咪幾好 唔出啲大問題 港豬就唔會反省點解捐極都唔夠 日撚日都告急"},{"pid":"2380391df0080f18634b92690ce4182f67775c2d","tid":458412,"uid":127203,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T22:47:47.000Z","msg":"有冇人知最後真係用晒，咁會點？<br />\n醫院係咪會同國內買血？ 定由得無血唔洗醫人就算？"},{"pid":"883c0055f517adce698bfe4bff6d025ca6d40735","tid":458412,"uid":49392,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T22:51:09.000Z","msg":"早兩年唔係吹到香港人要靠解放軍既血咩"},{"pid":"36b5eff0e88ac0bb1e9bf934cd81079191709c4f","tid":458412,"uid":72638,"like":108,"dislike":5,"score":103,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T